  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Acetabulum fracture are high energy trauma in young people as it can be the result of a
      simple fall in elder people. This fracture generates an incongruity between acetabulum and
      femoral head. So surgery is recognized as the best treatment even if technically difficult
      because of the the complexity of anatomy.Navigation is widely used in orthopaedic surgery .

      The aim of the study is to evaluate the effect of peroperative navigation system on
      reduction of the acetabulum articular surface
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
